text.div:
This value set includes codes based on the following rules:

  • Import all the codes that are contained in http://hl7.org/fhir/uv/ips/ValueSet/results-blood-group-uv-ips
  • Import all the codes that are contained in http://hl7.org/fhir/uv/ips/ValueSet/results-presence-absence-uv-ips
  • Import all the codes that are contained in http://hl7.org/fhir/uv/ips/ValueSet/results-microorganism-uv-ips

name: ResultsCodedValuesLaboratoryUvIps
title: Results Coded Values Laboratory - IPS
publisher: Health Level Seven International - Patient Care Work Group
description: This value set is defined as the union of: (a) Blood group [Type]; (b) Presence/Absence Indicators (2.16.840.1.113883.11.22.52) (c) Microorganisms (2.16.840.1.113883.11.22.49)
